recap.title: Implement new design from Library Communications

comments.body:
After reviewing my conversation with Stephanie, we should feel free to have some license to size the text for maximum readability on the web since the fonts in the PDF provided are tiny. There will need to be three templates:

1. Homepage (different only from top-level page because it includes the twitter block)
2. Top level page, need left aligned pinwheel with picture and right aligned pinwheel w/o image as a background graphic.
3. Second level page, left aligned pinwheel as background graphic.

 Two inconsistencies in the design that I'd leave alone.

1. The About menu drops off some of the pages, let's keep it.
2. Let's leave the dropdowns for second level pages as well.
